head_commit.message:
Remove instances of 'qsTrId("...close")', 'qsTrId("...back")', and 'qsTrId("...getHelp")  (#6422)

* Use 'MZI18n.GlobalGoBack' instead of 'qsTrId("vpn.main.back")'

* Add 'Get help' string to strings.yaml and use in templates

* Use MZI18n.GlobalClose in MZPopup.qml

* Remove a few additional instances of 'qsTrId(vpn.main.back)'

* Lint: Change getHelp string ID

* Lint roll
